DESCRIPTION: Moves members to the provided voice channel.
EXTENDED_LINE_1: **{{prefix}}move [Channel ID] @user @user** ~ Moves the users to the channel.
EXTENDED_LINE_2: **{{prefix}}move [Channel ID] [Channel ID]** ~ Moves all members from one channel to the other.
NEED_CHANNEL: You did not provide a channel to move to!
NEED_MEMBERS: You did not provide any members to move!
SUCCESS: Successfully moved the member's you requested!
